    "120d1c38-c539-4978-9a1b-8605dd93549a": {
      "type": "nine15--ctas",
      "settings": {
        "title": "The Power of Music: \n<h2>Courtney Santana</h2>",
        "text": "<b>October 2023</b><Br><br>\n\n<p>Our recent Consuela ACL takeover got us on a musical vibe. Today, we want to shine the spotlight on the incredible and talented Consuela Viva Babe Courtney! Her passion for music and her commitment to spreading positivity are truly awe-inspiring.\n\n<p>Courtney shares her musical gifts with the world and uses her platform to make a difference in her community. We are immensely grateful for the work she does and the impact she has on those around her.\n\n<p>In a recent interview, Courtney shared some valuable advice for other artists, encouraging them to trust themselves and embrace the power of their creations. She believes that art can touch hearts, uplift spirits, and even help individuals overcome difficult times.\n\n<p>We are incredibly inspired by Courtney's outlook on life and her commitment to making today ridiculously awesome for everyone she encounters. She truly embodies the spirit of the Viva Babe community and serves as an inspiration to us all.\n\n<p>Thank you, Consuela Viva Babe Courtney, for your musical talents, your light, and the positive influence you bring to your loved ones and community. Keep shining bright!</p>",
        "link_text": "Survive2Thrive",
        "link_url": "https://survive2thrivefoundation.org/",
        "button_text": "Hear Her Story",
        "button_url": "shopify://blogs/its-not-about-the-bag",
        "btn_style": "primary",
        "text_color": "#000000",
        "gradient": "",
